    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱马仕 (Hermes) 手袋需求强劲，销量超越古驰 (Gucci)</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/hermes-sales-climb-as-birkin-bag-maker-shows-resilience</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于铂金包制造商爱马仕 (Hermes) 的高价手袋需求强劲，其销售额出现上涨，顶住了奢侈品市场整体低迷的冲击，而古驰 (Gucci) 所有者开云集团 (Kering SA) 等同行也未能摆脱这种困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-24/hermes-sales-climb-as-birkin-bag-maker-shows-resilience</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 24 Oct 2024 06:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
